{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, some of my photographs were taken on her balcony in clothes she provided and toys that she had provided by virtue of having them already.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It must have been her children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't know, my mother doesn't know, nobody knows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hilde doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She doesn't remember who the person was, only that it was a woman doctor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She called Hilde on the second day and said, can't keep this child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This child prays in some funny gibberish stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's something not right here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was a devout Christian, which is why she couldn't have a heathen in her house and had to baptize me, however she did that, or whatever constituted baptism to her.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had been taught a night prayer, and that-- that was about all I knew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I wasn't saying the, God preserve me and Jesus look over me and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I learned that later at another place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we had to get rid of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, these are small details.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who could think of all these things?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I certainly didn't understand what I was saying and what it was for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to be moved from there real fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know with how many people I stayed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one really knows, because sometimes one would take me to the-- the next.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I became known to the parents of some of the university women students, like [GERMAN], as the illegitimate child of another student who didn't want anyone to know that she'd had a baby.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in those times, Hitler much advocated procreation.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
